span>) presents opportunities from the optimism surrounding Japan's stock market and the potential shift of its macroeconomic growth trajectory. Valuations for domestic equities and growth capacity concerning the sheer amount of corporate spare</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1824344345/image_1824344345.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747467-ewj-good-valuation-and-long-term-outlook-with-significant-short-term-risks-in-mind", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 16:33:32", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747001", "title": "Buy The Dip 2: Dividend Stocks Getting Way Too Cheap", "description": "<p></p> <figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"phrase buy the dip handwritten on night wet window glass surface\" data-id=\"1289941019\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"3648px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">z1b</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p></p> <p>Dividend stocks (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SCHD\" title=\"Schwab Strategic Trust - Schwab U.S. Dividend Equity ETF\">SCHD</a>) recently suffered a dip.</p> <p>Utilities (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XLU\" title=\"Utilities Select Sector SPDR\u00ae Fund ETF\">XLU</a>), MLPs (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MLPA\" title=\"Global X MLP ETF\">MLPA</a>), REITs (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VNQ\" title=\"Vanguard Real Estate ETF\">VNQ</a>), BDCs (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BIZD\" title=\"VanEck Vectors BDC Income ETF\">BIZD</a>) etc. all dropped after the Fed revised its guidance for rate cuts in 2025.</p> <p>They still expect to cut interest rates, but they explained that they</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747001-buy-the-dip-2-dividend-stocks-getting-way-too-cheap", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 16:25:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747464", "title": "DFI Retail's Sales Make The Stock A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cropped image of woman with shopping bags using a mobile phone\" data-id=\"836709534\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">RUNSTUDIO</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I like <strong>DFI Retail Group Holdings'</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DFILF\" title=\"DFI Retail Group Holdings Limited\">OTCPK:DFILF</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DFIHY\" title=\"DFI Retail Group Holdings Limited\">OTCPK:DFIHY</a>) (D01:SP) latest asset divestitures to retain a Buy rating for the name. Earlier, my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4706246-dfi-retail-a-beneficiary-of-health-and-convenience-trends-rating-upgrade\">July 24, 2024, article</a> touched on the favorable growth outlook for DFILF's \"convenience</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/836709534/image_836709534.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747464-dfi-retail-sales-make-stock-buy", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 16:17:35", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747463", "title": "Funko: Easy Money Has Been Made; Time To Downgrade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Row of figures of American company Funko Pop in the shop window\" data-id=\"961973282\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1082px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">kipgodi</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In a perfect world, investment opportunities would be perpetually attractive and would generate strong returns all the time. But that's not how this world works. Even the best prospects eventually achieve their easy upside, leaving more limited upside on the table. And if</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961973282/image_961973282.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747463-funko-easy-money-made-time-to-downgrade", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 16:10:29", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747462", "title": "Dollar Tree Stores: Short-Term Concerns But Still A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dollar Tree\" data-id=\"1265347025\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5886px\" height=\"3924px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment summary</h2> <p>My <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4704509-dollar-tree-stay-calm-and-remain-long-on-this-strong-operator\">previous investment thought</a> on Dollar Tree Stores (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DLTR\" title=\"Dollar Tree, Inc.\">DLTR</a></span>) (published on 17th July) was a buy rating because I believed it provided investors good exposure to the uncertain macro conditions back then, and that valuation was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265347025/image_1265347025.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747462-dollar-tree-stores-short-term-concerns-but-still-a-buy", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 16:02:43", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747367", "title": "2 Places To Put Your Money If The Fed Raises Rates In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"2025 spelled with golden numerals and zero is replaced with a piggy bank\" data-id=\"2183192528\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Since the Fed lowered interest rates last month by another 25 basis points, the overall market has seemingly not agreed with that decision. Uncertainty within the bond markets has caused the 2-year and 10-year treasuries to experience volatility. In</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2183192528/image_2183192528.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747367-2-places-to-put-your-money-if-the-fed-raises-rates-in-2025", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 15:47:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747458", "title": "Royal Caribbean Cruises: Why You Should Disembark", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Royal Caribbean, Navigator of the Seas cruise ship and tender boat\" data-id=\"1712186363\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">sanfel/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>I give Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RCL\" title=\"Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd.\">RCL</a></span>) a sell rating because the company has poor short-term liquidity, a massive amount of long-term debt, and is overvalued by 227% from its current intrinsic value of $70.48, much of which is due to the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1712186363/image_1712186363.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747458-royal-caribbean-cruises-why-you-should-disembark", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 15:38:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747353", "title": "TKO Group: WWE Evolution Continues With Netflix Shift", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"WWE World Wrestling Entertainment American professional fake wrestling promotion company headquarters in Stamford Connecticut.\" data-id=\"2163043433\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1068px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163043433/image_2163043433.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploa